      • extractAnnotatedPeaks

        public java.util.List<AnnoPeak> extractAnnotatedPeaks(Spectrum spec,
                                                      double tol,
                                                      java.lang.String unit,
                                                      int maxCS)
        Extract annotated peaks of PSM
        Parameters:
        spec - Spectrum to get Annotated Peaks
        tol - size of the tolerance
        unit - tolerance unit to consider. if "ppm" then consider ppm tolerance, if "da" then consider da tolerance
        maxCS - maximum fragment charge state to consider. Current maximum possible fragment charge is 2.
        Returns:
        List of AnnoPeak object
